{"tid":1706363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望各位醒醒，唔好再自欺欺人，警甴有槍跟本就冇問題","createTime":"2019-11-11T05:21:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T10:26:22.000Z","uid":62151,"like":71,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"bfb6e5c3c1416f402401b02c95d3b0bb5245d86f","tid":1706363,"uid":62151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T05:21:15.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你冇槍永遠先係問題所在<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n當大家有<span style=\"color: blue;\">對等武力</span>嘅時候,班警甴都只係廢物<br />\n即刻嚇撚到瓹翻入老母個閪到<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2384869584973573\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2384869584973573&d=30k2sE%2FAiGmcVOPaBnjddWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=b1d75a46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2384869584973573</a><br />\n<br />\n同場加映烏克蘭<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OW1QM0f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOW1QM0f.png&h=2eba5399&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>手拉式除草機<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XjA92p2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXjA92p2.png&h=ab719ec3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>輕巧型除草機連教學<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thehomegunsmith.com/pdf/12g-pistol.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehomegunsmith.com%2Fpdf%2F12g-pistol.pdf&d=30k2sE%2FAiGmcVOPaBnjddWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=df36aa71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.thehomegunsmith.com/pdf/12g-pistol.pdf</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eTionpn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeTionpn.png&h=6555719d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>喇叭牌正露丸膠囊裝<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thehomegunsmith.com/pdf/EHF_Shotgun_Ammo_Book.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehomegunsmith.com%2Fpdf%2FEHF_Shotgun_Ammo_Book.pdf&d=30k2sE%2FAiGmcVOPaBnjddWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=a28753c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.thehomegunsmith.com/pdf/EHF_Shotgun_Ammo_Book.pdf</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fhBJnpo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfhBJnpo.png&h=d6355c6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X2hTKCJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX2hTKCJ.png&h=847598e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n＊PRIMER可以有好多替代品<br />\n上而鋁罐下至膠紙都得，任君選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n氣壓水管<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thehomegunsmith.com/pdf/AIR-POWERED-PCP_ARROW_RIFLE.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehomegunsmith.com%2Fpdf%2FAIR-POWERED-PCP_ARROW_RIFLE.pdf&d=30k2sE%2FAiGmcVOPaBnjddWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=bee47dd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.thehomegunsmith.com/pdf/AIR-POWERED-PCP_ARROW_RIFLE.pdf</a><br />\n[quote]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SOfibif.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSOfibif.png&h=36143dc5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n詳情及其他教學：<a href=\"http://www.thehomegunsmith.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehomegunsmith.com%2F&d=30k2sE%2FAiGmcVOPaBnjddWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=5246a994\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.thehomegunsmith.com/</a>"},{"pid":"a80c180468c86e13ba956780517f22a94346d523","tid":1706363,"uid":62151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T05:22:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ed95ff0018a946e754037aed5dfbf81af6a620","tid":17